import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { WebsocketService } from '../websocket.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-testsocket', templateUrl: './testsocket.component.html', styleUrls: ['./testsocket.component.css'] }) export class TestsocketComponent { constructor(private webSocketService: WebsocketService) {} data : number[] = [2,4,5,6,2,8,10]; ngOnInit(): void { this.webSocketService.connect().subscribe((data) => { this.data = data; console.log(data); }); } sendDataToServer(): void { this.webSocketService.sendData(this.data); } }
